<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
{% include 'partials/_meta.j2' %}
</head>
<body>
{% include 'partials/_header.j2' %}

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <p class="hero-eyebrow">E-commerce · Fintech · AI · <span class="hero-eyebrow-date">{{ today_str }}</span></p>
                <h1 class="hero-title">The three sectors reshaping how value moves.</h1>
                <p class="hero-lede">A daily distillation of the most consequential moves across e-commerce, fintech, and AI — read by 42,000+ operators, builders, and investors.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="topics">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="topics-head reveal">
                    <h2>Three verticals. One daily read.</h2>
                    <p>Pick a section to dive in — or subscribe to get the cross-sector digest in your inbox every weekday.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="topic-grid">
                    <a href="ecommerce.html" class="topic-card reveal">
                        <svg class="topic-glyph" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M5 7h14l-1 14H6L5 7z"/>
                            <path d="M9 7V5a3 3 0 0 1 6 0v2"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h3>E-commerce</h3>
                        <p>Marketplaces, DTC brands, retail media, logistics, and the operators reshaping how goods move online.</p>
                        <div class="topic-latest">Latest</div>
                        <p class="topic-snippet">{{ snippets.ecommerce }}</p>
                        <div class="topic-cta">Explore E-commerce</div>
                    </a>

                    <a href="fintech.html" class="topic-card reveal">
                        <svg class="topic-glyph" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/>
                            <path d="M14.5 9.5h-3.5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-3.5"/>
                            <path d="M12 7v1.5"/>
                            <path d="M12 16.5V18"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h3>Fintech</h3>
                        <p>Payments, banking, stablecoins, embedded finance, and the rails carrying the next trillion in commerce.</p>
                        <div class="topic-latest">Latest</div>
                        <p class="topic-snippet">{{ snippets.fintech }}</p>
                        <div class="topic-cta">Explore Fintech</div>
                    </a>

                    <a href="ai.html" class="topic-card reveal">
                        <svg class="topic-glyph" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M12 2.5l1.5 8L22 12l-8.5 1.5L12 22l-1.5-8.5L2 12l8.5-1.5L12 2.5z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h3>AI</h3>
                        <p>Foundation models, agents, infrastructure, and the businesses being rebuilt around a new compute curve.</p>
                        <div class="topic-latest">Latest</div>
                        <p class="topic-snippet">{{ snippets.ai }}</p>
                        <div class="topic-cta">Explore AI</div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

{% include 'partials/_subscribe.j2' %}
    </main>

{% include 'partials/_footer.j2' %}
</body>
</html>
